{"tid":1411051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥批評訴求已變質有人肆無忌憚提光復香港","createTime":"2019-08-05T02:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T06:50:36.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"77a3e773beb1f5860fe96c50d4a29cce5f413522","tid":1411051,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:53:14.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥表示，政府並非沒有回應訴求，她在早前的記者會上已表明，修例工作已經完全停止，而且不會再啟動。<br />\n<br />\n她反問，一些民間的訴求中，是否一個法治社會認同和爭取的要求，包括釋放從事好多違法活動的被埔人士，她又批評，訴求已經變質，有人明顯肆無忌憚提出光復香港的口號，挑戰一國兩制，形容要將香港「推冧」，希望市民珍惜現有的生活，縱容暴力只會令激進人士更使用暴力，妨礙社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n對於警隊處理衝突手法的問題，林鄭月娥表示，已啟動現有法定和獨立機制審視，相信監警會主席按照法定權力處理和跟進。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，釋放被捕人士並不是她的權力，是律政司司長在不受干預下進行的決定，希望市民諒解。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472707-20190805.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472707-20190805.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=UCNXK7Cjp0Jh61Qt1camEP5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=1bf08c74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472707-20190805.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=84e641d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472707-20190805.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"288da418b5199e92fd317024fb9939f2bceee33a","tid":1411051,"uid":55851,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgyxweW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgyxweW.gif&h=e46d3678&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2934f44ef208e0794cc4878ebb983b06e81b5f65","tid":1411051,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class